metadata.name: STATE OF BLUE
metadata.description:
Over the past few years, I've learnt a lot and gone through both joy and pain, which has taught me to move on. Even if I sometimes fail, I still manage to make it and continue. Whatever happens, I'll keep going on like I always have.

NYTCOOLCAT ,2021
